{"tid":1838921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】扯開醫護人員口罩吐口水播菌 病人︰我活不了你們都別想活！","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T11:58:48.000Z","uid":148874,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec522ca2e9e1bbe934ba8d9a302a2b8dd18b931c","tid":1838921,"uid":148874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情擴散全國，除源頭疫區湖北外，河北昨日（23日）亦出現首宗死亡個案，令死亡人數增至18人。現時各地醫院診所大排長龍，醫護人員疲於奔命，但有河北石家莊的醫護人員卻未獲病人體諒，當地一名發燒病人近日到醫院求診，竟發惡扯脫醫護人員的口罩，更向對方吐口水，揚言：「我活不了，你們都別想活！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKMv2di.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKMv2di.jpg&h=7ec0eb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲疑似醫護人員指被病人吐口水 (圖片來源︰微博截圖)<br />\n<br />\n有內地網民昨日（23日）在微博分享一張疑似與醫護人員好友對話截圖。該醫護人員任職於河北石家莊的醫院，因武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，當地所有醫護人員均不準放假。他在院內遇到一名疑似發燒病人時，擔心病人間交叉感染，好心向對方遞上口罩，當時委婉地說：「醫院病人多，你現在不舒服抵抗力低，給你一個口罩帶上吧。」<br />\n<br />\n未料病人隨即情緒失控，向他大聲怒吼：指「啊我生病了，你給我口罩有用嗎？」說罷即將他臉上的口罩扯下，並對她吐口水「播菌」，再補一句︰<br />\n<br />\n「我不活了，你們都別想活。」<br />\n該名醫護人員事後悲訴「我哭了」，形容這是入職以來第一次哭。他被吐後去了洗面，現需於醫院接受隔離，但仍樂觀地指：「不過我覺得沒啥事，那病人可能是單純的發燒。」<br />\n<br />\n醫療資源緊張令醫患衝突不斷，微博又瘋傳武漢有疑似醫生爆料指其同僚工作期間，遭病人家屬撕開防護服，更指：<br />\n「憑甚麼穿著防護服？要死一起死！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ySvhMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ySvhMU.jpg&h=9692808c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有傳醫護人員被病者家屬撕開防護服。 (圖片來源︰微博截圖) <br />\n<br />\n撰文：潘迦晴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2550359/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%89%AF%E9%96%8B%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4%E6%92%AD%E8%8F%8C%20%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%EF%B8%B0%E6%88%91%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E9%83%BD%E5%88%A5%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2550359%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2589%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2590%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E8%258F%258C%2520%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25B4%25BB%25EF%25BC%2581&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=496413b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2550359/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%89%AF%E9%96%8B%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4%E6%92%AD%E8%8F%8C%20%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%EF%B8%B0%E6%88%91%E6%B4%BB%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E9%83%BD%E5%88%A5%E6%83%B3%E6%B4%BB%EF%BC%81</a>"},{"pid":"317803f3ab2920a814b3b22ffc5b7e6e5acb7d61","tid":1838921,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"170c07a4fad877aef23fc84b29d50ca1c6d3bc32","tid":1838921,"uid":60393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"做得好！期待支那人滅族"},{"pid":"a213e86bcb3ed5891013bba5a84a24858cbc6f91","tid":1838921,"uid":162060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10Y2TjS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10Y2TjS.gif&h=7e033610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6fdfc0282ff08776637c9600ea809ab637847ef","tid":1838921,"uid":148874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"支持武漢同胞攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df870279f5d17fc3b66a6d64ad9433c85c27441a","tid":1838921,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"一路好走<br />\n下世唔好再喺中國出世了"},{"pid":"1e329b45ce13d4652a0cf6b4ea4ec672222